extends layout

block content
  .homepage.home
    .page
      .container
        .row
          .col-sm-12
            video#bgvid(autoplay='autoplay', loop='loop', poster='images/polina.jpg')
              source(src='images/polina.mp4', type='video/mp4')



    div(style='background-color: #dfdfdf;')
      .container(style='padding: 50px 0 10px 0;')
        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .work-box.stamfordauction
              .row
                .col-sm-6.description
                  h1 Stamford Auction
                  h2 Website Design
                  p
                    | Stamford Auction is an antique auction house located in Bridgeport, CT.
                  p
                    | I helped Stamford Auction with the design of their homepage, where they wanted to showcase some of their recently sold items and offer services.
                  p
                    a(href='project.html?project=stamfordauction') View Details
                .col-sm-6.example
                  a(href='project.html?project=stamfordauction')
                    img(src='images/home_sa.jpg', class='img-responsive')
        
        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .work-box.blackrockgalleries
              .row
                .col-sm-6.description
                  h1 Black Rock Galleries
                  h2 Website Design & Development
                  p
                    | Black Rock Galleries is an antique shop in Bridgeport, CT.
                  p
                    | I helped Black Rock Galleries with their website design and front-end development.
                  p
                    a(href='project.html?project=blackrockgalleries') View Details
                .col-sm-6.example
                  a(href='project.html?project=blackrockgalleries')
                    img(src='images/home_brg.jpg', class='img-responsive')

        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .work-box.headliner
              .row
                .col-sm-6.description
                  h1 Headliner.fm
                  h2 Website Design & Development
                  p
                    | Headliner.fm is a web application that helps brands and businesses promote each other on Facebook and Twitter.
                  p
                    | At headliner.fm I designed and coded the website and web application user interface.
                  p
                    a(href='project.html?project=headliner') View Details
                .col-sm-6.example
                  a(href='project.html?project=headliner')
                    img(src='images/home_headliner.jpg', class='img-responsive')

        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .work-box.maps
              .row
                .col-sm-6.description
                  h1 Maps of Imaginary Places
                  h2 Creator
                  p
                    | Maps of Imaginary Places is a print shop that makes geometric posters, iPhone cases and laptop skins.
                  p
                    | This is my hobby where I can experiment with the interaction of shape and color.  I had a great time putting this collection together and I wanted to share it, I hope you enjoy them!
                  p
                    a(href='project.html?project=maps') View Details
                .col-sm-6.example
                  a(href='project.html?project=maps')
                    img(src='images/home_maps.png', class='img-responsive')

        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .work-box.nabbr
              .row
                .col-sm-6.description
                  h1 Nabbr.com
                  h2 Interface Designer and Developer
                  p
                    | Nabbr.com, now Selectable Media, was an online video network that created custom promotional widgets and distributed them to more than to 40 Million Gen-Y social web users each month.
                  p
                    | I was responsible for designing widget interfaces, creating
                    | custom skins and planning marketing strategies for a variety of
                    | clients including Sony BMG, Warner Music Group, Universal Studios,
                    | MTV and many others.
                  p
                    a(href='project.html?project=nabbr') View Details
                .col-sm-6.example
                  a(href='project.html?project=nabbr')
                    img(src='images/home_nabbr.jpg', class='img-responsive')

        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .work-box.goldenhour
              .row
                .col-sm-6.description
                  h1 Goldenhour FX
                  h2 Creator
                  p
                    | After wishing there was Instagram for Mac Photo Booth, I decided to just make some effects myself. They're free to download.
                  p
                    a(href='project.html?project=golden') View Details
                .col-sm-6.example
                  a(href='project.html?project=golden')
                    img(src='images/home_golden.jpg', class='img-responsive')
        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .work-box.viewall
              .row
                .col-sm-12.description.text-center
                  h1(style='margin: 0px 0px 20px 0px;') Other Projects
                  p I've worked on many other projects, more work coming soon!
                  p
                    a(href='project.html?project=web') View Site
